==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: insightful
<hw>insightful</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>having intellectual
depth; having or showing an exceptional degree of insight{2}; -- of
people or their comments.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> thoughtful.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>characterized by sympathetic
understanding.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> discerning, understanding.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>having a keen intellect.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> prehensile.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>insightfulness</ent>⟦br⟧
